label.value: adult Drosulfakinin neuron of pars intercerebralis

value.value: Drosulfakinin neuron with its soma in the adult pars intercerebralis. These neurons are a subset of the insulin secreting cells (Soderberg et al., 2012; Wu et al., 2019).

label.value: larval Drosulfakinin neuron of pars intercerebralis

value.value: Drosulfakinin neuron with its soma in the larval pars intercerebralis. These neurons are a subset of the insulin secreting cells (Soderberg et al., 2012).

definition.value: Park et al. (2008) suggest complete overlap of Dsk and Ilp (in 7 cells) in the PI.

label.value: larval mushroom body one-step feedback neuron

value.value: Larval neuron that is postsynaptic to a mushroom body output neuron and presynaptic to a mushroom body input neuron (Eschbach et al., 2020).

label.value: larval mushroom body two-step feedback neuron

value.value: Larval neuron that is postsynaptic to a one-step feedback neuron, but not reliably postsynaptic to a mushroom body output neuron, and is presynaptic to a mushroom body input neuron (Eschbach et al., 2020).
Larval neuron that is presynaptic to a mushroom body input neuron, but does not receive reliable input from a mushroom body output neuron, or a mushroom body feedback neuron (Eschbach et al., 2020).

label.value: larval mushroom body feed across neuron

value.value: Larval neuron that is postsynaptic to a mushroom body output neuron and presynaptic to a mushroom body input neuron in a different compartment of the mushroom body, but does not reliably connect input and output neurons of the same compartment (Eschbach et al., 2020).

label.value: adult allatostatin A neuron of superior lateral protocerebrum

value.value: Allatostatin A-expressing neuron of the adult that has its cell body in the superior lateral protocerebrum (Ni et al., 2019). These neurons are glutamatergic and express the Allatostatin A neuropeptide (Ni et al., 2019). Their activation increases sleep upstream of ExFl2 neurons, to which they synapse in the superior medial protocerebrum (Ni et al., 2019).

definition.value: Synapsing shown by GRASP and functional data (Ni et al., 2019).

label.value: larval mushroom body one-step feedback neuron 1

value.value: Larval mushroom body one-step feedback neuron that receives synaptic input from FBN-28, MBON-d1 and MBON-j1 and outputs onto FAN-2 and FAN-3 (Eschbach et al., 2020). There is one bilateral pair of these cells (Eschbach et al., 2020).
